*Operacije* su postale rutinski zadatak za medicinski tim. (Operations have become a routine task for the medical team.)

Hirurzi su obavili *operaciju* na prednjem delu grudi. (Surgeons performed an operation on the front of the chest.)

Bolnica je imala najmoderniju opremu za *operacije*. (The hospital had the most modern equipment for operations.)

Lekari su morali da se spreme za *operaciju*. (The doctors had to prepare for the operation.)

Oni su uspešno izvršili *operaciju*. (They successfully performed the operation.)